tags.description: Non-Teslas can charge here. Charging cables use the Tesla MagicDock, so each cable contains both a NACS (Tesla) plug and a CCS Combo1 (type1_combo) adapter plug, but only one plug can be used at a time.
tags.name: Tesla Supercharger
